Okay, cut!
Nice!

17
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:00,350
We'll make
that cat talk!

18
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:02,480
He's a witch's cat,
after all.

19
00:01:02,620 --> 00:01:04,990
So he should at least make one
or two snide remarks, right?

20
