How absurd.

21
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:11,090
Your name is Shamisen! Come on,
Shamisen, say something!

22
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:15,200
There's no way he'd talk.
Actually, please don't talk.

23
00:01:15,430 --> 00:01:17,300
Wait, "Shamisen"!?

24
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,570
Hmm, pretty good.

25
00:01:20,870 --> 00:01:23,970
Kyon, I'm going to leave
that cat's care to you.

26
00:01:24,110 --> 00:01:25,540
Take him home
with you.

27
00:01:25,940 --> 00:01:28,380
You have until tomorrow to
teach him a trick or two.

28
